## Development


### Running test application.

Here you can check admin and API endpoints.

```
python3 -m venv venv
. venv/bin/activate
pip install -e .[test]
./manage.py runserver
```


### Running tests

```
# Without coverage report
make test

# With coverage report
make test-cov
```


### Deploying new version

Change version in `setup.cfg` and push new tag to main branch.

```
git tag 0.0.x
git push --tags
```

